</IN>
<LP>
   HUDSON, Ohio -- Alltel Corp. said shareholders have
approved its previously announced acquisition of Systematics
Inc.
   Under terms of the agreement, each Systematics share will
be exchanged for 1.325 shares of Alltel common.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Alltel is a telephone holding company. Systematics is a
maker of software for financial institutions.
